title: Sing Out Cambridge: first rehearsal of term
description:
Join Sing Out Cambridge, Cambridge’s LGBT+ Community Choir, for our first rehearsal back after a summer break. We’d love to see some new faces, so please do come along! We are a non-audition choir and no choral experience is necessary.

Email cambslgbtchoir@gmail.com for more information, and find us on Facebook at SingOutCambridge.
